PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780790574
OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,FThe strikes come as the Trump
OL,7,Fadministration increases pressure on
OL,8,FIran in efforts to force a deal to end
OL,9,Fthe conflict.
OL,11,FUS Central Command said on social
OL,12,Fmedia Friday night that Iran fired
OL,13,Fseven ballistic missiles toward Kuwait
OL,14,Fand Bahrain, with US forces
OL,15,Fintercepting six of the missiles and a
OL,16,Fseventh failing to reach its target.
OL,18,FThe military said there were no
OL,19,Freports of harm to US personnel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780790574
OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,FThe ballistic missiles were fired
OL,7,Fafter the US earlier in the day shot
OL,8,Fdown four Iranian drones that were
OL,9,Flaunched toward the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,11,F"The attack drones posed an immediate
OL,12,Fthreat to regional maritime traffic,"
OL,13,FUS Central Command said on social
OL,14,Fmedia.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@eO]
