OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,FKuwait's military said forces were
OL,7,Fintercepting missiles and drones
OL,8,Fattacking the country, while Bahrain
OL,9,Factivated air raid sirens and told
OL,10,Fresidents to move to the nearest safe
OL,11,Flocation and follow official
OL,12,Finstructions.
OL,14,FIran's Revolutionary Guard said it
OL,15,Ftargeted the Ali Al Salem airbase,
OL,16,Fwhich hosts U. forces in Kuwait, and
OL,17,Fthe US Navy's 5th Fleet in the tiny
OL,18,FGulf island nation of Bahrain,
OL,19,Faccording to the state-run IRNA news
OL,20,Fagency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
