OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780790574
OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,FThe US military is enforcing a
OL,7,Fblockade on Iranian ports in response
OL,8,Fto Tehran's chokehold on the crucial
OL,9,Fcorridor for global oil and natural
OL,10,Fgas shipments, which has sent energy
OL,11,Fprices spiking and posed political
OL,12,Fproblems for President Donald Trump's
OL,13,FRepublican Party ahead of the midterm
OL,14,Fcongressional elections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780790574
OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,FThe strikes are the latest in back-and-
OL,7,Fforth attacks that have strained the
OL,8,Ftenuous ceasefire in the war and
OL,9,Fefforts to reach a deal to extend that
OL,10,Ftruce. Earlier this week, Iranian
OL,11,Fdrones heavily damaged a passenger
OL,12,Fterminal at Kuwait's main airport,
OL,13,Fkilling one person, wounding dozens
OL,14,Fand briefly closing the airfield.
OL,16,FDespite the attacks raising new
OL,17,Fconcerns that the ceasefire could
OL,18,Fcollapse, Trump told reporters on
OL,19,FFriday that "the situation with Iran
OL,20,Fseems to be going quite well.
OL,26,@{D@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780790574
OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,F"We're going to come out of Iran very
OL,7,Fquickly, and it's going to be very
OL,8,Fstrong one way or the other, whether
OL,9,Fit's a piece of paper or the very
OL,10,Ftough way," Trump said at an event
OL,11,Fwith farmers in Wisconsin.
OL,13,F"The very tough way is maybe the
OL,14,Feasier way, but we're going to come
OL,15,Fout, and your fertiliser prices are
OL,16,Fgoing to go way down, just like they
OL,17,Fwere four months ago."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]uD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
