PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780790574
OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,FUS and Iranian negotiators reached a
OL,7,Ftentative agreement a week ago to
OL,8,Fextend the ceasefire by 60 days and
OL,9,Fstart a new round of talks on Iran's
OL,10,Fnuclear program. But Trump has called
OL,11,Ffor unspecified changes, and Iranian
OL,12,Fofficials have shown no public signs
OL,13,Fof signing off on the deal.
OL,15,FAsked on Friday why it was taking so
OL,16,Flong, Trump told NBC's "Meet the
OL,17,FPress" it was because "it's a very
OL,18,Fhard thing for them," citing their
OL,19,F"great independence" and the fact that
OL,20,F"they're strong, they're proud."
OL,26,@xD@XOUyD@FO]yD@WOUzD@UO]{D@AOU{D@TO]|D@
OL,26,AAOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
