OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780790574
OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,F"There are things they never thought
OL,7,Fthey'd be doing that they're going to
OL,8,Fhave to do. They've got no choice, and
OL,9,Fit takes a little while," he said in
OL,10,Fthe interview.
OL,12,FTrump said the Iranians still have 21%
OL,13,Fto 22% of their missiles.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@YO]
