OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780790574
OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,FThe Trump administration has also
OL,7,Ftaken credit for the latest ceasefire
OL,8,Fagreed this week by the Lebanese
OL,9,Fgovernment and Israel after US-
OL,10,Fbrokered talks in Washington. However,
OL,11,Fthe Iranian-backed Hezbollah militant
OL,12,Fgroup has rejected the agreement, and
OL,13,Fnew attacks have put it at further
OL,14,Frisk.
OL,16,FThe Israeli military on Friday struck
OL,17,Fmultiple parts of southern Lebanon and
OL,18,Fissued evacuation warnings for nine
OL,19,Fvillages, including one that has
OL,20,Fsheltered thousands of people
OL,21,Fdisplaced by the fighting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780790574
OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,FThe strikes killed nine people in six
OL,7,Flocations in southern Lebanon, the
OL,8,Fstate news agency reported.
OL,10,FThe Israeli military said two soldiers
OL,11,Fwere wounded, one severely, in an
OL,12,Fencounter on Friday with militants in
OL,13,Fsouthern Lebanon.
OL,15,FThe fighting in Lebanon, where Israeli
OL,16,Fforces have seized large swaths of the
OL,17,Fsouth, also threatens efforts to end
OL,18,Fthe Iran war and reopen the Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz because Iran has demanded that
OL,20,Fany lasting truce extend to Lebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780790574
OL,3,CUS intercepts Iranian drones targeting
OL,4,CGulf states, in test of shaky ceasefire
OL,6,FBesides the drone interception in the
OL,7,FStrait of Hormuz, the US military said
OL,8,Fearlier on Friday that its forces
OL,9,Fboarded a sanctioned oil tanker linked
OL,10,Fto Iran in the Indian Ocean as the
OL,11,FUnited States seeks to prevent Iran
OL,12,Ffrom profiting off its oil and other
OL,13,Fgoods.
OL,15,FThe US also targeted Iran's energy
OL,16,Fsector with new sanctions on a group
OL,17,Fof people, firms and tankers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
